  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Few patients who have major risk factors develop Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS).
      The heritable determinants might be the reason. The multicenter study is to investigate the
      association between ARDS and polymorphism in ARDS gene r.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Few patients who have major risk factors develop ARDS. The heritable determinants might be
      the reason. The multicenter study is to investigate the association between ARDS and
      polymorphism in ARDS gene. Meanwhile, the association between ARDS and different methods of
      therapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
